OL,3,C'I thought I was Superman': Inside
OL,4,CBritain's steroid boom
OL,6,FITV's Tonight programme found out that
OL,7,Fpeople are increasingly reaching out
OL,8,Fto performance-enhancing drugs experts
OL,9,Fto mitigate the dangerous side effects
OL,10,Fof taking a range of drugs, as Antoine
OL,11,FAllen reports
OL,13,F"The only time I was really happy was
OL,14,Fwhen I was in that gym or I was
OL,15,Finjecting or taking a tablet."
OL,17,FZak Wilkinson became addicted to
OL,18,Fsteroids. After years of abusing
OL,19,Fperformance-enhancing drugs, he nearly
OL,20,Fdied after falling into a coma.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
