OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774458668
OL,3,C'I thought I was Superman': Inside
OL,4,CBritain's steroid boom
OL,6,FITV's Tonight programme has been told
OL,7,Fthere are believed to be over one
OL,8,Fmillion performance-enhancing drug and
OL,9,Fanabolic steroid users in the UK, with
OL,10,Fmore people turning to tablets and
OL,11,Finjections to become fitter and
OL,12,Fstronger.
OL,14,FThis is all despite clear NHS advice
OL,15,Fwarning against using these drugs
OL,16,Fwithout a prescription.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774458668
OL,3,C'I thought I was Superman': Inside
OL,4,CBritain's steroid boom
OL,6,FYet, few understand the dangers of
OL,7,Fperformance-enhancing drugs more than
OL,8,FZak, who started abusing steroids and
OL,9,Fother performance-enhancing drugs as a
OL,10,Fteenage boy.
OL,12,FBy the time he was an adult, he was
OL,13,Ftaking 17 performance-enhancing drug
OL,14,Finjections and 49 tablets a week.
OL,16,FThe cost was more than just financial.
OL,17,FHis addiction nearly ended his life.
OL,19,FAfter collapsing in his sister's
OL,20,Fliving room, he spent seven days in a
OL,21,Fcoma in the hospital.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
