OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774458668
OL,3,C'I thought I was Superman': Inside
OL,4,CBritain's steroid boom
OL,6,F"Eyes have rolled to the back of my
OL,7,Fhead. I'm having a seizure on the
OL,8,Ffloor. And luckily enough, the
OL,9,Fambulance was a two-minute drive
OL,10,Fbecause any longer and it would have
OL,11,Fbeen straight into a cardiac arrest,"
OL,12,Fhe said.
OL,14,F"The only time I was really happy was
OL,15,Fwhen I was in that gym or I was
OL,16,Finjecting or taking a tablet," Zak
OL,17,Ftells ITV's Tonight programme
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
