OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774458668
OL,3,C'I thought I was Superman': Inside
OL,4,CBritain's steroid boom
OL,6,FZak is now in recovery and spends his
OL,7,Ftime mentoring other addicts and
OL,8,Fwarning others about the dangers of
OL,9,Fmisuse.
OL,11,FHe continues to love fitness, but he
OL,12,Fkeeps himself occupied with amateur
OL,13,Fboxing. He fears going back to the
OL,14,Fdark days of steroid addiction.
OL,16,F"Every day I wake up and I would love
OL,17,Fto put an injection in my ass because
OL,18,FI'm still in my recovery. It's an
OL,19,Fuphill battle," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
