OL,3,C'I thought I was Superman': Inside
OL,4,CBritain's steroid boom
OL,6,FHis story is rarely shown on social
OL,7,Fmedia, but it is a stark warning to
OL,8,Fthose chasing the so-called "perfect
OL,9,Fbody".
OL,11,FThe Tonight programme has uncovered a
OL,12,Fboom in the use of steroids and other
OL,13,Fperformance-enhancing drugs, with
OL,14,Fsocial media becoming an encyclopedia
OL,15,Fof unregulated information about how
OL,16,Fto buy and use drugs, alongside a
OL,17,Fgrowing market of research chemicals
OL,18,Fcalled peptides.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774458668
OL,3,C'I thought I was Superman': Inside
OL,4,CBritain's steroid boom
OL,6,FThe world of anabolic steroids and
OL,7,Fperformance-enhancing drugs is no
OL,8,Flonger restricted to bodybuilders and
OL,9,Felite athletes.
OL,11,FTonight followed Rafal Skrzypczak, a
OL,12,Ffactory worker from Yorkshire, who
OL,13,Fallowed ITV to film him preparing his
OL,14,Finjections in his kitchen, as if he
OL,15,Fwere simply making a cup of tea.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774458668
OL,3,C'I thought I was Superman': Inside
OL,4,CBritain's steroid boom
OL,6,F"If it wasn't for a guy on YouTube, I
OL,7,Fwouldn't have the confidence to do
OL,8,Fthis," he said. "I have 250 milligrams
OL,9,Fof NPP (Nandrolone Phenylpropionate)
OL,10,Fand 250 milligrams of testosterone...
OL,11,FI do this two times a week only."
OL,13,FHe said the drugs transformed his life
OL,14,Fand body.
OL,16,F"I went from being exhausted all the
OL,17,Ftime at work and in life, to full of
OL,18,Fenergy," he added.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
