PN,30809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774458668
OL,3,C'I thought I was Superman': Inside
OL,4,CBritain's steroid boom
OL,6,FBut going down this path comes at a
OL,7,Fcost. Rafal now requires regular check-
OL,8,Fups with a drug specialist.
OL,10,FSuch services are seeing a major shift
OL,11,Fin users.
OL,13,FGareth Balmer, National Harm Reduction
OL,14,FLead at the support charity WithYou,
OL,15,Fsaid: "We're now seeing in many of our
OL,16,Fneedle exchanges, which were
OL,17,Ftraditionally where we would see
OL,18,Fheroin and cocaine injectors, but in
OL,19,Fmany areas now it's anabolic
OL,20,Fsteroids... they're outnumbering
OL,21,Ftraditional users."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
