OL,3,C'I thought I was Superman': Inside
OL,4,CBritain's steroid boom
OL,6,FLike thousands of others, Raf buys his
OL,7,Fdrugs on the black market.
OL,8,FIncreasingly, this is done online.
OL,10,FExperts say the number is growing each
OL,11,Fyear, fuelled by social media
OL,12,Finfluencers tapping into fears about
OL,13,Fageing and desires for strength,
OL,14,Fyouth, and perfection.
OL,16,FAfter just a few clicks, the algorithm
OL,17,Fbegins to feel personal, asking
OL,18,Fleading questions that drive people to
OL,19,Fsign up to questionable drug protocols
OL,20,Fand advice:
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
