OL,3,C'I thought I was Superman': Inside
OL,4,CBritain's steroid boom
OL,6,F"Are you always tired?"
OL,8,F"Has your sex drive plummeted?"
OL,10,F"Do you want to feel stronger than
OL,11,Fever?"
OL,13,FIn podcasts, the conversations go even
OL,14,Ffurther. Even Joe Rogan has spoken
OL,15,Fopenly about his own use.
OL,17,F"Add a little bit of growth hormone,
OL,18,Fadd a little bit of testosterone..."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
