OL,3,C'I thought I was Superman': Inside
OL,4,CBritain's steroid boom
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FFor months, I have been investigating
OL,12,Fthe UK's booming market in steroids
OL,13,Fand performance-enhancing drugs,
OL,14,Fspeaking to users, dealers, and
OL,15,Fmedical experts.
OL,17,FSteroids themselves are nothing new,
OL,18,Fbut what people are taking now, and
OL,19,Fhow far they are willing to go, is
OL,20,Fchanging.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774458668
OL,3,C'I thought I was Superman': Inside
OL,4,CBritain's steroid boom
OL,6,FIncreasingly, users are turning to
OL,7,F"stacks" ` combinations of drugs `
OL,8,Falongside a new wave of substances
OL,9,Fknown as peptides.
OL,11,FScientifically, peptides are small
OL,12,Fchains of amino acids that the body
OL,13,Fnaturally produces. They send signals
OL,14,Fthat control how the body functions.
OL,16,FBut online, they are being marketed
OL,17,Ffor muscle growth, fat loss, recovery,
OL,18,Fand even anti-ageing, often without
OL,19,Fsolid scientific backing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30814
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774458668
OL,3,C'I thought I was Superman': Inside
OL,4,CBritain's steroid boom
OL,6,FOne creator told his audience, "I'm
OL,7,Fgoing to continue to put my body on
OL,8,Fthe line for the community," before
OL,9,Finjecting a syringe on camera.
OL,11,FYou may not recognise the term, but
OL,12,Fyou already know some peptides.
OL,13,FInsulin is one. So are the new
OL,14,Fgeneration of weight loss drugs now
OL,15,Fbeing prescribed clinically.
OL,17,FThe global peptide therapeutics market
OL,18,Fwas worth around $46.4 billion (#34.59
OL,19,Fbillion) in 2024 and could reach $100
OL,20,Fbillion (#74.5 billion) by 2034,
OL,21,Faccording to Global Market Insights.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30815
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774458668
OL,3,C'I thought I was Superman': Inside
OL,4,CBritain's steroid boom
OL,6,FWhile regulated drugs are transforming
OL,7,Fobesity treatment, a parallel market
OL,8,Fis emerging online.
OL,10,FNames like Reta, BPC 157, TB 500, and
OL,11,FGHK Cu are widely discussed across
OL,12,Fsocial media, with claims they can
OL,13,Fheal injuries, build muscle, and even
OL,14,Fimprove appearance.
OL,16,FMany are sold under the disclaimer
OL,17,F"for research purposes only".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30816
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774458668
OL,3,C'I thought I was Superman': Inside
OL,4,CBritain's steroid boom
OL,6,FDespite the supposed benefits,
OL,7,Fpeptides sit in a legal grey area.
OL,8,FRegulators say these drugs aren't fit
OL,9,Ffor ` and can't be sold for ` human
OL,10,Fconsumption.
OL,12,FOne user told me: "BPC 157 and TB
OL,13,Fblend. It's the injury healing blend,
OL,14,Fotherwise known as the Wolverine
OL,15,FStack."
OL,17,FWe found listings on Amazon, the
OL,18,Fworld's largest online retailer,
OL,19,Fadvertising products as peptides, such
OL,20,Fas BPC 157 and TB 500, packaged to
OL,21,Fresemble standard food supplements.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30817
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774458668
OL,3,C'I thought I was Superman': Inside
OL,4,CBritain's steroid boom
OL,6,FLaboratory testing commissioned by ITV
OL,7,Fidentified no detectable trace of the
OL,8,Fadvertised peptides in a sampled
OL,9,Fproduct. Following our findings,
OL,10,FAmazon said it had removed the
OL,11,Flistings.
OL,13,FITV's Tonight programme found peptides
OL,14,Fsold on Amazon that aren't meant for
OL,15,Fhuman consumption
OL,17,FIn a statement, Amazon told ITV
OL,18,FTonight: "Safety is our top priority,
OL,19,Fand we require all products offered in
OL,20,Four store to comply with applicable
OL,21,Flaws, regulations and Amazon policies.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30818
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774458668
OL,3,C'I thought I was Superman': Inside
OL,4,CBritain's steroid boom
OL,6,F"Amazon does not allow the sale of
OL,7,Funlicensed medicines, and this item
OL,8,Fhas been removed.
OL,10,F"We are continuously monitoring our
OL,11,Fstore and if we discover a product
OL,12,Fundetected by our checks, we update
OL,13,Fand retrain our machine learning
OL,14,Fmodels to improve detection."
OL,16,FDoctors warn that the risks of the
OL,17,Funregulated sale of drugs are
OL,18,Fsignificant.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30819
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774458668
OL,3,C'I thought I was Superman': Inside
OL,4,CBritain's steroid boom
OL,6,FDr Honor Townshend said: "The reality
OL,7,Fis, because these substances are not
OL,8,Fregulated, you can't guarantee what
OL,9,Fyou've bought online is actually what
OL,10,Fyou've received."
OL,12,FAt the same time, prescriptions for
OL,13,Ftestosterone replacement therapy,
OL,14,Fknown as TRT, are rising sharply.
OL,16,FUnlike many drugs in the PED world,
OL,17,FTRT is a legitimate treatment for men
OL,18,Fwith clinically confirmed low
OL,19,Ftestosterone, but NHS guidelines are
OL,20,Fstrict.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30820
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774458668
OL,3,C'I thought I was Superman': Inside
OL,4,CBritain's steroid boom
OL,6,FPatients must undergo repeated blood
OL,7,Ftests and meet clear medical criteria.
OL,8,FYet long waiting lists and demand have
OL,9,Fpushed some towards private clinics
OL,10,Fand online providers, with costs
OL,11,Freaching up to #300 a month.
OL,13,FDoctors warn that where there is money
OL,14,Fto be made, there is also potential
OL,15,Ffor exploitation.
OL,17,FThey are clear: TRT should not be used
OL,18,Fas a lifestyle drug or performance
OL,19,Fenhancer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G20/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30821
SC,0021
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774458668
OL,3,C'I thought I was Superman': Inside
OL,4,CBritain's steroid boom
OL,6,FZak's story shows where this road can
OL,7,Flead.
OL,9,FThe more "superhuman" physiques online
OL,10,Fare normalised, the greater the
OL,11,Fpressure for faster results. And for
OL,12,Fsome, that pursuit ends not in
OL,13,Fperfection, but in addiction, serious
OL,14,Fhealth consequences, or worse.
OL,16,FOne of the biggest dangers with PEDs
OL,17,Fis the unregulated black-market sales,
OL,18,Fincorrect dosages, and unsafe
OL,19,Fproduction of the drugs, which can be
OL,20,Fcontaminated or simply mixed with
OL,21,Fother substances.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G21/25
