OL,3,C'I thought I was Superman': Inside
OL,4,CBritain's steroid boom
OL,6,FAgainst this backdrop, the world's
OL,7,Fmost controversial sports competition
OL,8,Fis set to take place.
OL,10,FThe Enhanced Games are expected to
OL,11,Fstart in May in Las Vegas.
OL,13,FIt will have allowed elite athletes to
OL,14,Ftake a range of performance-enhancing
OL,15,Fdrugs, such as testosterone, hormone
OL,16,Freplacement therapy and some peptides,
OL,17,Funder a medical trial in Abu Dhabi.
OL,19,FAll the drugs offered to athletes have
OL,20,Fto be approved by the FDA, the US drug
OL,21,Fregulator.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G22/25
